'''Ezekiel Lovecraft''' sells and buys fish and bait in the town of [[Witchaven]]. He sells all normal [[Fishing]] equipment from his shop called [[Lovecraft's Tackle]].

His skin is a sickly yellow colour, similar to the villagers possessed by [[sea slug]]s, but he lacks the gills and bulging eyes that they also possess.

==Slug Menace==
During the [[Slug Menace]] [[quest]], he gives the player [[Page 2]] of [[Brother Maledict]]'s holy book, which he mysteriously received by someone who pushed it under his door, most likely agents of the [[Sea Slugs]] like [[Mayor Hobb]], Brother Maledict, or [[Col. Jake O'Niall]] as these pages are used to craft special runes to be used as keys to free [[Mother Mallum]] from her imprisonment.

