==Trivia==
*Ezekial's last name is a reference to the famous American author of horror, fantasy and science fiction, [[wikipedia:H. P. Lovecraft|Howard Phillips ("H.P.") Lovecraft]]. Ezekial mentions his family have always been either bait sellers or writers, and mentions his relative Howard. This is further confirmed by the nature of the quests he's involved in.
*Instead of "Trade", like all other shop owners, he has a right-click option "Shop" that opens the shop's window.

